                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT W.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(partition by W."IdAbs", W."IdRol", W."IdStare" ORDER BY W."IdAbs" DESC, W."IdRol" DESC, W."IdStare" DESC) "IdRow" FROM "Ptj_CereriDrepturi" W) DR ON (DR."IdAbs" = A."IdAbsenta" OR DR."IdAbs" = -13) AND (DR."IdStare" = A."IdStare" OR DR."IdStare" = -13) AND (DR."IdRol" = A."Rol" OR DR."IdRol" = -13) AND (DR."IdActiune" = 3 OR DR."IdActiune" = -13) AND DR."IdRow" <= 1
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",

                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99

                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99

                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2

                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION

                                )

                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +

                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                (
                                -99
                                )

                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +

                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                -99
                                )

                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"

                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2

                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION

                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                -99
                                )

                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"

                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra14" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra14" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra14" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=14) + '=' + "CampExtra14" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra15" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra15" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra15" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=15) + '=' + "CampExtra15" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra16" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra16" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra16" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=16) + '=' + "CampExtra16" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=17) + '=' + "CampExtra17" + '; ' ELSE '' END +

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=20) + '=' + "CampExtra20" + '; ' ELSE '' END +

                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                (
                                -99
                                )

                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra15" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra15" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra15" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=15) + '=' + "CampExtra15" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra16" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra16" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra16" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=16) + '=' + "CampExtra16" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra17" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=17) + '=' + "CampExtra17" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra18" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=18) + '=' + "CampExtra18" + '; ' ELSE '' END +

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra20" <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=1 AND "IdCampExtra"=20) + '=' + "CampExtra20" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                                CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                                SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", DR."Valoare" AS Anulare_Valoare, DR."NrZile" AS Anulare_NrZile, COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa"
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                -99
                                )

                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

Eroarea:   SELECT B."Rol", B.F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + A.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10017 AS CNP, A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii", A.F10023 AS "DataPlecarii",
                        A.F10011 AS "NrContract", CAST(A.F10043 AS int) AS "Norma",A.F100901, CASE WHEN (A.F10025 = 0 OR A.F10025=999) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "AngajatActiv",
                        X.F71804 AS "Functia", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie",G.F00406 AS "Filiala",H.F00507 AS "Sectie",I.F00608 AS "Departament", B."RolDenumire"  
                        FROM (
                        SELECT A.F10003, 0 AS "Rol", COALESCE((SELECT COALESCE("Alias", "Denumire") FROM "tblSupervizori" WHERE "Id"=0),'Angajat') AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        WHERE A.F10003 = 
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, B."IdSuper" AS "Rol", CASE WHEN D."Alias" IS NOT NULL AND D."Alias" <> '' THEN D."Alias" ELSE D."Denumire" END AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" B ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        INNER JOIN "Ptj_Circuit" C ON B."IdSuper" = -1 * c."UserIntrod" 
                        LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" D ON D."Id" = B."IdSuper"
                        WHERE B."IdUser"= 
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, 76 AS "Rol", 'Fara rol' AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "Ptj_Circuit" C ON C."UserIntrod"= ) B
                        INNER JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN F718 X ON A.F10071=X.F71802
                        LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                        LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                        LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                        LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607

Data:    11.10.2019 11:11:12
Pagina:    General
Eveni:     IncarcaDT
Eroarea:   SELECT * FROM (
                            SELECT CAST(A.F10003 AS INT) AS "Marca",A.F10017 AS "CNP",A.F10008 + ' ' + A.F10009 AS "NumeComplet",
                            E.F00204 AS "Companie",F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie",G.F00406 AS "Filiala",H.F00506 AS "Sectie",I.F00607 AS "Departament", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",
                            CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 900 THEN '#ffff8000' ELSE CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 999 THEN '#dc96dc' ELSE (CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 0 THEN (CASE WHEN (A.F100925 <> 0 AND F100922 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100922 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= F100923 AND GETDATE() <= F100924) THEN '#ffffffc8' ELSE CASE WHEN (A.F100915 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= A.F100916) THEN '#FF0066FF' ELSE '#ffc8ffc8' END END) ELSE '#ffffc8c8' END) END END AS "Culoare",
                            CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 900 THEN 'Candidat' ELSE CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 999 THEN 'Angajat in avans' ELSE (CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 0 THEN (CASE WHEN (A.F100925 <> 0 AND F100922 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100922 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= F100923 AND GETDATE() <= F100924) THEN 'Activ suspendat' ELSE CASE WHEN (A.F100915 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= A.F100916) THEN 'Activ detasat' ELSE 'Activ' END END) ELSE 'Inactiv' END) END END AS "Stare",
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10083,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Str. ' + a.F10083 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10084,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Nr. ' + a.F10084 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10085,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Bloc. ' + a.F10085 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F100892,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Sc. ' + a.F100892 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F100893,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Et. ' + a.F100893 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10081,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Oras. ' + a.F10081 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10082,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Sect. ' + a.F10082 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F100891,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE CASE WHEN  (UPPER(a.F100891) like '%JUDET%' OR UPPER(a.F100891) like '%MUNICIPIU%') THEN ' ' + a.F100891 ELSE  ' Judet. ' + a.F100891 END END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10087,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Cod Postal. ' + a.F10087 END) AS "AdresaCompleta"
                             
                            FROM F100 A
                            LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202 
                            LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304 
                            LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405 
                            LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506 
                            LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607 
                             
                            WHERE 1=1  AND A.F10003 IN (SELECT CAST(F10003 AS INT) AS F10003 FROM USERS WHERE F70102 = 5
                            UNION
                            SELECT B.F10003 FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                            INNER JOIN "MP_relGrupSuper" C ON B."IdGrup" = C."IdGrup"
                             inner join f100 e on b.F10003=e.F10003 
                            WHERE C."IdSuper" = 5  AND ( e.F10025 = 0  OR  e.F10025 = 999 )
                            UNION
                            SELECT CAST(B.F10003 AS INT) AS F10003 FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                            INNER JOIN "MP_relGrupSuper" C ON B."IdGrup" = C."IdGrup"
                            INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" D ON B.F10003=D.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = -1 * D."IdSuper"
                             inner join f100 e on b.F10003=e.F10003 
                            WHERE D."IdUser" = 5  AND ( e.F10025 = 0  OR  e.F10025 = 999 ))
                            ) X WHERE 1=1  AND ( "Stare"='Activ' OR  "Stare"='Angajat in avans')
                            ORDER BY "NumeComplet"

Eroarea:   SELECT * FROM (
                            SELECT CAST(A.F10003 AS INT) AS "Marca",A.F10017 AS "CNP",A.F10008 + ' ' + A.F10009 AS "NumeComplet",
                            E.F00204 AS "Companie",F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie",G.F00406 AS "Filiala",H.F00506 AS "Sectie",I.F00607 AS "Departament", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",
                            CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 900 THEN '#ffff8000' ELSE CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 999 THEN '#dc96dc' ELSE (CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 0 THEN (CASE WHEN (A.F100925 <> 0 AND F100922 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100922 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= F100923 AND GETDATE() <= F100924) THEN '#ffffffc8' ELSE CASE WHEN (A.F100915 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= A.F100916) THEN '#FF0066FF' ELSE '#ffc8ffc8' END END) ELSE '#ffffc8c8' END) END END AS "Culoare",
                            CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 900 THEN 'Candidat' ELSE CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 999 THEN 'Angajat in avans' ELSE (CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 0 THEN (CASE WHEN (A.F100925 <> 0 AND F100922 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100922 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= F100923 AND GETDATE() <= F100924) THEN 'Activ suspendat' ELSE CASE WHEN (A.F100915 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= A.F100916) THEN 'Activ detasat' ELSE 'Activ' END END) ELSE 'Inactiv' END) END END AS "Stare",
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10083,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Str. ' + a.F10083 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10084,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Nr. ' + a.F10084 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10085,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Bloc. ' + a.F10085 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F100892,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Sc. ' + a.F100892 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F100893,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Et. ' + a.F100893 END) +

                            (CASE WHEN a.F100897 is null or a.F100897 = 0 THEN '' ELSE case when niv3.tip in (11, 19, 22, 23) then ' sat ' + niv3.denloc else
                            case when niv3.tip = 6 and upper(niv3.denloc) not like '%SECTOR%' then ' sector ' + niv3.DENLOC else ' ' + niv3.denloc end END end) +

                            (case when a.F100914 is null or a.F100914 = 0 THEN '' else case when niv2.tip in (1, 4) and UPPER(niv2.DENLOC) not like '%MUNICIPIU%' then ' municipiul ' + niv2.DENLOC else
                            case when niv2.tip = 2 and UPPER(niv2.DENLOC) not like '%ORAS%' then ' orasul ' + niv2.DENLOC else 
                            case when niv2.TIP = 3 and upper(niv2.DENLOC) not like '%COMUNA%' then ' comuna ' + niv2.DENLOC else ' ' + niv2.denloc end end end end ) +

                            (CASE WHEN a.F100921 is null or a.F100921 = 0 THEN '' ELSE case when upper(niv1.denloc) like '%JUDET%' or upper(niv1.denloc)  like '%MUNICIPIU%' then ' ' + niv1.DENLOC else
                             case when upper(niv1.denloc) like '%BUCURESTI%' then ' municipiul ' + niv1.DENLOC else ' judetul ' + niv1.denloc end end END) +
                            

                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10087,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Cod Postal. ' + a.F10087 END) AS "AdresaCompleta"
                             
                            FROM F100 A
                            LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202 
                            LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304 
                            LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405 
                            LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506 
                            LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607 
                             
                            WHERE 1=1  AND A.F10003 IN (SELECT CAST(F10003 AS INT) AS F10003 FROM USERS WHERE F70102 = 2
                            UNION
                            SELECT B.F10003 FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                            INNER JOIN "MP_relGrupSuper" C ON B."IdGrup" = C."IdGrup"
                             inner join f100 e on b.F10003=e.F10003 
                            WHERE C."IdSuper" = 2  AND ( e.F10025 = 0  OR  e.F10025 = 999 )
                            UNION
                            SELECT CAST(B.F10003 AS INT) AS F10003 FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                            INNER JOIN "MP_relGrupSuper" C ON B."IdGrup" = C."IdGrup"
                            INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" D ON B.F10003=D.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = -1 * D."IdSuper"
                             inner join f100 e on b.F10003=e.F10003 
                            WHERE D."IdUser" = 2  AND ( e.F10025 = 0  OR  e.F10025 = 999 ))
                            ) X WHERE 1=1  AND ( "Stare"='Activ' OR  "Stare"='Angajat in avans')
                            ORDER BY "NumeComplet"

                        FROM F100 A
                        WHERE A.F10003 = 2 AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Avs_Circuit" WHERE "Super1"=0) > 0
                        UNION

                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" B ON A.F10003=B.F10003

                        LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" D ON D."Id" = B."IdSuper"
                        WHERE B."IdUser"=2

                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "Avs_Circuit" C ON C."Super1"=2

                        INNER JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN F002 C ON A.F10002 = C.F00202
                        LEFT JOIN F718 X ON A.F10071=X.F71802
                        LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                        LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405

                                GROUP BY A."Continut"

Eroarea:   SELECT  B."Rol", B."RolDenumire", A.F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + A.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", 
                        X.F71804 AS "Functia", C.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie",G.F00406 AS "Filiala",H.F00507 AS "Sectie",I.F00608 AS "Departament" 
                        FROM (
                        SELECT A.F10003, 0 AS "Rol", COALESCE((SELECT COALESCE("Alias", "Denumire") FROM "tblSupervizori" WHERE "Id"=0),'Angajat') AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        WHERE A.F10003 = 100 AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Avs_Circuit" WHERE "Super1"=0) > 0
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, B."IdSuper" AS "Rol", CASE WHEN D."Alias" IS NOT NULL AND D."Alias" <> '' THEN D."Alias" ELSE D."Denumire" END AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" B ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        INNER JOIN "Avs_Circuit" C ON B."IdSuper" = -1 * c."Super1"
                        LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" D ON D."Id" = B."IdSuper"
                        WHERE B."IdUser"=100
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, 76 AS "Rol", 'Fara rol' AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "Avs_Circuit" C ON C."Super1"=100
                        ) B
                        INNER JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN F002 C ON A.F10002 = C.F00202
                        LEFT JOIN F718 X ON A.F10071=X.F71802
                        LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                        LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                        LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                        LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
						WHERE A.F10025 IN (0, 999)

                        WHERE A.F10003 = 100 AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Avs_Circuit" WHERE "Super1"=0) > 0
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, B."IdSuper" AS "Rol", CASE WHEN D."Alias" IS NOT NULL AND D."Alias" <> '' THEN D."Alias" ELSE D."Denumire" END AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" B ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        INNER JOIN "Avs_Circuit" C ON B."IdSuper" = -1 * c."Super1"
                        LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" D ON D."Id" = B."IdSuper"
                        WHERE B."IdUser"=100
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, 76 AS "Rol", 'Fara rol' AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "Avs_Circuit" C ON C."Super1"=100
                        ) B
                        INNER JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN F002 C ON A.F10002 = C.F00202
                        LEFT JOIN F718 X ON A.F10071=X.F71802
                        LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                        LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                        LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                        LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
						WHERE A.F10025 IN (0, 999)

Eveni:     IncarcaDT
Eroarea:   SELECT  B."Rol", B."RolDenumire", A.F10003, A.F10008 + ' ' + A.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", 
                        X.F71804 AS "Functia", C.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie",G.F00406 AS "Filiala",H.F00507 AS "Sectie",I.F00608 AS "Departament" 
                        FROM (
                        SELECT A.F10003, 0 AS "Rol", COALESCE((SELECT COALESCE("Alias", "Denumire") FROM "tblSupervizori" WHERE "Id"=0),'Angajat') AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        WHERE A.F10003 =  AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Avs_Circuit" WHERE "Super1"=0) > 0
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, B."IdSuper" AS "Rol", CASE WHEN D."Alias" IS NOT NULL AND D."Alias" <> '' THEN D."Alias" ELSE D."Denumire" END AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" B ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        INNER JOIN "Avs_Circuit" C ON B."IdSuper" = -1 * c."Super1"
                        LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" D ON D."Id" = B."IdSuper"
                        WHERE B."IdUser"=
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, 76 AS "Rol", 'Fara rol' AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "Avs_Circuit" C ON C."Super1"=
                        ) B
                        INNER JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN F002 C ON A.F10002 = C.F00202
                        LEFT JOIN F718 X ON A.F10071=X.F71802
                        LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                        LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                        LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                        LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
						WHERE A.F10025 IN (0, 999)

                                INNER JOIN (SELECT F10003 , [2019-11-01] AS "Ziua1", [2019-11-02] AS "Ziua2", [2019-11-03] AS "Ziua3", [2019-11-04] AS "Ziua4", [2019-11-05] AS "Ziua5", [2019-11-06] AS "Ziua6", [2019-11-07] AS "Ziua7", [2019-11-08] AS "Ziua8", [2019-11-09] AS "Ziua9", [2019-11-10] AS "Ziua10", [2019-11-11] AS "Ziua11", [2019-11-12] AS "Ziua12", [2019-11-13] AS "Ziua13", [2019-11-14] AS "Ziua14", [2019-11-15] AS "Ziua15", [2019-11-16] AS "Ziua16", [2019-11-17] AS "Ziua17", [2019-11-18] AS "Ziua18", [2019-11-19] AS "Ziua19", [2019-11-20] AS "Ziua20", [2019-11-21] AS "Ziua21", [2019-11-22] AS "Ziua22", [2019-11-23] AS "Ziua23", [2019-11-24] AS "Ziua24", [2019-11-25] AS "Ziua25", [2019-11-26] AS "Ziua26", [2019-11-27] AS "Ziua27", [2019-11-28] AS "Ziua28", [2019-11-29] AS "Ziua29", [2019-11-30] AS "Ziua30" FROM 
                                (SELECT F10003, ValStr, Ziua From Ptj_Intrari_2 WHERE '2019-11-01' <= CAST(Ziua AS date) AND CAST(Ziua AS date) <= '2019-11-30') AS source  
                                PIVOT  (MAX(ValStr) FOR Ziua IN (  [2019-11-01], [2019-11-02], [2019-11-03], [2019-11-04], [2019-11-05], [2019-11-06], [2019-11-07], [2019-11-08], [2019-11-09], [2019-11-10], [2019-11-11], [2019-11-12], [2019-11-13], [2019-11-14], [2019-11-15], [2019-11-16], [2019-11-17], [2019-11-18], [2019-11-19], [2019-11-20], [2019-11-21], [2019-11-22], [2019-11-23], [2019-11-24], [2019-11-25], [2019-11-26], [2019-11-27], [2019-11-28], [2019-11-29], [2019-11-30] )) pvt
                                ) pvt ON X.F10003=pvt.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=X.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN F1001 B ON A.F10003=B.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT R.F10003, MIN(R.Ziua) AS ZiuaMin FROM Ptj_Intrari_2 R WHERE YEAR(R.Ziua)= 2019 AND MONTH(R.Ziua)= 11 GROUP BY R.F10003) Q ON Q.F10003=A.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Intrari_2 Y ON A.F10003=Y.F10003 AND Y.Ziua=Q.ZiuaMin
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_tblStariPontaj K ON K.Id = ISNULL(X.IdStare,1) 
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Contracte C on C.Id = Y.IdContract 
                                LEFT JOIN F089 DR ON DR.F08902 = A.F1009741 
                                LEFT JOIN viewCategoriePontaj CTG ON A.F10003 = CTG.F10003
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiNorma(X.F10003, '2019-11-30') dn 
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiDataPlecare(X.F10003, '2019-11-30') ddp 

							    LEFT JOIN F002 S2 ON Y.F10002 = S2.F00202
							    LEFT JOIN F003 S3 ON Y.F10004 = S3.F00304
							    LEFT JOIN F004 S4 ON Y.F10005 = S4.F00405

							    LEFT JOIN F005 H ON Y.F10006 = H.F00506
							    LEFT JOIN F006 I ON Y.F10007 = I.F00607

							    LEFT JOIN F007 S7 ON B.F100958 = S7.F00708
                                LEFT JOIN F008 S8 ON B.F100959 = S8.F00809

                                LEFT JOIN F062 L ON Y.F06204Default=L.F06204

                                LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802

                                WHERE X.An = 2019 AND X.Luna = 11 
                                ORDER BY AngajatNume) A
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A.F10003 IN ( SELECT X.F10003 FROM (  SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup WHERE C.IdSuper =4 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.f10003 UNION SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup INNER JOIN F100Supervizori D ON D.F10003 = B.F10003 AND D.IdSuper = (-1 * C.IdSuper) AND (100 * 2019 + 11 BETWEEN isnull(100 * year(D.DataInceput) + MONTH(D.DataInceput), 190000) AND isnull(100 * year(D.DataSfarsit) + MONTH(D.DataSfarsit), 210000))  WHERE D.IdUser =4 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.F10003) X  WHERE X.F10003 IN (SELECT S.F10003 FROM F100 S WHERE CONVERT(date,S.F10022) <> CONVERT(date,S.F100993)  AND F10022 <= '2019-11-30' AND '2019-11-01' <= F100993 ) GROUP BY X.F10003)

                                A.F10078 AS Angajator, DR.F08903 AS TipContract, 
                                (SELECT MAX(US.F70104) FROM USERS US WHERE US.F10003=X.F10003) AS EID,
                                dn.Norma AS AvansNorma, 
                                CASE WHEN Y.Norma <> dn.Norma THEN (SELECT MAX(F70406) FROM F704 WHERE F70403=pvt.F10003 AND F70404=6 AND YEAR(F70406)=2019 AND MONTH(F70406)=9) ELSE '2100-01-01' END AS AvansData,
                                L.F06205, Fct.F71804 AS Functie,
                                X.* ,COALESCE("Ziua1",'') AS "Ziua1",COALESCE("Ziua2",'') AS "Ziua2",COALESCE("Ziua3",'') AS "Ziua3",COALESCE("Ziua4",'') AS "Ziua4",COALESCE("Ziua5",'') AS AS "Ziua17",COALESCE("Ziua18",'') AS "Ziua18",COALESCE("Ziua19",'') AS "Ziua19",COALESCE("Ziua20",'') AS "Ziua20",COALESCE("Ziua21",'') AS "Ziua21",COALESCE("Ziua22",'') AS numeric(10)) AS "F20_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F21",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F21_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F22",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F22_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F23",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F23_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F24",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F24_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F25",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F25_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F26",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F26_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F27",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F27_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F28",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F28_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F29",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F29_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F30",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F30_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F31",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F31_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F32",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F32_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F33",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F33_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F34",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F34_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F35",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F35_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F36",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F36_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F37",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F37_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F38",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F38_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F39",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F39_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F40",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F40_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F41",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F41_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F42",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F42_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F43",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F43_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F44",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F44_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F45",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F45_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F46",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F46_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F47",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F47_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F48",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F48_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F49",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F49_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F50",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F50_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F51",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F51_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F52",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F52_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F53",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F53_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F54",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F54_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F55",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F55_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F56",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F56_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F57",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F57_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F58",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F58_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F59",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F59_Tmp",CAST(COALESCE(X."F60",0) AS numeric(10)) AS "F60_Tmp"
                                FROM Ptj_Cumulat X 
		                        LEFT JOIN Ptj_tblStari st on st.Id = x.IdStare
		                        left join SituatieZileAbsente zabs on zabs.F10003 = x.F10003 and zabs.An = x.An and zabs.IdAbsenta = (select Id from Ptj_tblAbsente where DenumireScurta = 'CO')
		                        left join SituatieZLP zlp on zlp.F10003 = x.F10003 and zlp.An = x.An
                                INNER JOIN (SELECT F10003 , [2019-09-01] AS "Ziua1", [2019-09-02] AS "Ziua2", [2019-09-03] AS "Ziua3", [2019-09-04] AS "Ziua4", [2019-09-05] AS "Ziua5", [2019-09-06] AS "Ziua6", [2019-09-07] AS "Ziua7", [2019-09-08] AS "Ziua8", [2019-09-09] AS "Ziua9", [2019-09-10] AS "Ziua10", [2019-09-11] AS "Ziua11", [2019-09-12] AS "Ziua12", [2019-09-13] AS "Ziua13", [2019-09-14] AS "Ziua14", [2019-09-15] AS "Ziua15", [2019-09-16] AS "Ziua16", [2019-09-17] AS "Ziua17", [2019-09-18] AS "Ziua18", [2019-09-19] AS "Ziua19", [2019-09-20] AS "Ziua20", [2019-09-21] AS "Ziua21", [2019-09-22] AS "Ziua22", [2019-09-23] AS "Ziua23", [2019-09-24] AS "Ziua24", [2019-09-25] AS "Ziua25", [2019-09-26] AS "Ziua26", [2019-09-27] AS "Ziua27", [2019-09-28] AS "Ziua28", [2019-09-29] AS "Ziua29", [2019-09-30] AS "Ziua30" FROM 
                                (SELECT F10003, ValStr, Ziua From Ptj_Intrari_2 WHERE '2019-09-01' <= CAST(Ziua AS date) AND CAST(Ziua AS date) <= '2019-09-30') AS source  
                                PIVOT  (MAX(ValStr) FOR Ziua IN (  [2019-09-01], [2019-09-02], [2019-09-03], [2019-09-04], [2019-09-05], [2019-09-06], [2019-09-07], [2019-09-08], [2019-09-09], [2019-09-10], [2019-09-11], [2019-09-12], [2019-09-13], [2019-09-14], [2019-09-15], [2019-09-16], [2019-09-17], [2019-09-18], [2019-09-19], [2019-09-20], [2019-09-21], [2019-09-22], [2019-09-23], [2019-09-24], [2019-09-25], [2019-09-26], [2019-09-27], [2019-09-28], [2019-09-29], [2019-09-30] )) pvt
                                ) pvt ON X.F10003=pvt.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=X.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN F1001 B ON A.F10003=B.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT R.F10003, MIN(R.Ziua) AS ZiuaMin FROM Ptj_Intrari_2 R WHERE YEAR(R.Ziua)= 2019 AND MONTH(R.Ziua)= 9 GROUP BY R.F10003) Q ON Q.F10003=A.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Intrari_2 Y ON A.F10003=Y.F10003 AND Y.Ziua=Q.ZiuaMin
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_tblStariPontaj K ON K.Id = ISNULL(X.IdStare,1) 
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Contracte C on C.Id = Y.IdContract 
                                LEFT JOIN F089 DR ON DR.F08902 = A.F1009741 
                                LEFT JOIN viewCategoriePontaj CTG ON A.F10003 = CTG.F10003
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiNorma(X.F10003, '2019-09-30') dn 
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiDataPlecare(X.F10003, '2019-09-30') ddp 

							    LEFT JOIN F002 S2 ON Y.F10002 = S2.F00202
							    LEFT JOIN F003 S3 ON Y.F10004 = S3.F00304
							    LEFT JOIN F004 S4 ON Y.F10005 = S4.F00405

							    LEFT JOIN F005 H ON Y.F10006 = H.F00506
							    LEFT JOIN F006 I ON Y.F10007 = I.F00607

							    LEFT JOIN F007 S7 ON B.F100958 = S7.F00708
                                LEFT JOIN F008 S8 ON B.F100959 = S8.F00809

                                LEFT JOIN F062 L ON Y.F06204Default=L.F06204

                                LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802

                                WHERE X.An = 2019 AND X.Luna = 9 
                                ORDER BY AngajatNume) A
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A.F10003 IN ( SELECT X.F10003 FROM (  SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup WHERE C.IdSuper =4 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.f10003 UNION SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup INNER JOIN F100Supervizori D ON D.F10003 = B.F10003 AND D.IdSuper = (-1 * C.IdSuper) AND (100 * 2019 + 9 BETWEEN isnull(100 * year(D.DataInceput) + MONTH(D.DataInceput), 190000) AND isnull(100 * year(D.DataSfarsit) + MONTH(D.DataSfarsit), 210000))  WHERE D.IdUser =4 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.F10003) X  WHERE X.F10003 IN (SELECT S.F10003 FROM F100 S WHERE CONVERT(date,S.F10022) <> CONVERT(date,S.F100993)  AND F10022 <= '2019-9-30' AND '2019-9-01' <= F100993 ) GROUP BY X.F10003)

Eroarea:   SELECT F10003,F70103, F70114, "Mail", "IdLimba" ,
                                                            CASE WHEN 
                                                            COALESCE(CAST((SELECT COALESCE("Valoare",'0') FROM "tblParametrii" WHERE "Nume" = 'NrMinuteDeblocareParola' ) AS INT), 0) >0  AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM F100 Y WHERE Y.F10003=X.F10003 AND Y.F10025 IN (0,999)) > 0
                                                            THEN 
                                                            CASE WHEN
                                                             DATEDIFF(MINUTE,COALESCE([BLOCKTIME],convert(datetime,'1980-01-01 00:00:00',120)),GETDATE())  >= 
                                                            COALESCE(CAST((SELECT COALESCE("Valoare",'0') FROM "tblParametrii" WHERE "Nume" = 'NrMinuteDeblocareParola' ) AS INT), 0) 
                                                            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
                                                            ELSE 0 
                                                            END DEBLOCARE  
                                                            FROM USERS X WHERE UPPER(F70104)='HR'

                                                            COALESCE(CAST((SELECT COALESCE("Valoare",'0') FROM "tblParametrii" WHERE "Nume" = 'NrMinuteDeblocareParola' ) AS INT), 0) >0  AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM F100 Y WHERE Y.F10003=X.F10003 AND Y.F10025 IN (0,999)) > 0
                                                            THEN 
                                                            CASE WHEN
                                                             DATEDIFF(MINUTE,COALESCE([BLOCKTIME],convert(datetime,'1980-01-01 00:00:00',120)),GETDATE())  >= 
                                                            COALESCE(CAST((SELECT COALESCE("Valoare",'0') FROM "tblParametrii" WHERE "Nume" = 'NrMinuteDeblocareParola' ) AS INT), 0) 
                                                            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
                                                            ELSE 0 
                                                            END DEBLOCARE  
                                                            FROM USERS X WHERE UPPER(F70104)='ADMIN'

                                (SELECT F10003, ValStr, Ziua From Ptj_Intrari_2 WHERE '2019-11-01' <= CAST(Ziua AS date) AND CAST(Ziua AS date) <= '2019-11-30') AS source  
                                PIVOT  (MAX(ValStr) FOR Ziua IN (  [2019-11-01], [2019-11-02], [2019-11-03], [2019-11-04], [2019-11-05], [2019-11-06], [2019-11-07], [2019-11-08], [2019-11-09], [2019-11-10], [2019-11-11], [2019-11-12], [2019-11-13], [2019-11-14], [2019-11-15], [2019-11-16], [2019-11-17], [2019-11-18], [2019-11-19], [2019-11-20], [2019-11-21], [2019-11-22], [2019-11-23], [2019-11-24], [2019-11-25], [2019-11-26], [2019-11-27], [2019-11-28], [2019-11-29], [2019-11-30] )) pvt
                                ) pvt ON X.F10003=pvt.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=X.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN F1001 B ON A.F10003=B.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT R.F10003, MIN(R.Ziua) AS ZiuaMin FROM Ptj_Intrari_2 R WHERE YEAR(R.Ziua)= 2019 AND MONTH(R.Ziua)= 11 GROUP BY R.F10003) Q ON Q.F10003=A.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Intrari_2 Y ON A.F10003=Y.F10003 AND Y.Ziua=Q.ZiuaMin
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_tblStariPontaj K ON K.Id = ISNULL(X.IdStare,1) 
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Contracte C on C.Id = Y.IdContract 
                                LEFT JOIN F089 DR ON DR.F08902 = A.F1009741 
                                LEFT JOIN viewCategoriePontaj CTG ON A.F10003 = CTG.F10003

                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiDataPlecare(X.F10003, '2019-11-30') ddp 

							    LEFT JOIN F002 S2 ON Y.F10002 = S2.F00202
							    LEFT JOIN F003 S3 ON Y.F10004 = S3.F00304
							    LEFT JOIN F004 S4 ON Y.F10005 = S4.F00405

							    LEFT JOIN F005 H ON Y.F10006 = H.F00506
							    LEFT JOIN F006 I ON Y.F10007 = I.F00607

							    LEFT JOIN F007 S7 ON B.F100958 = S7.F00708

                                LEFT JOIN F062 L ON Y.F06204Default=L.F06204

                                LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802

                                WHERE X.An = 2019 AND X.Luna = 11 
                                ORDER BY AngajatNume) A

Eroarea:   with ptj_intrari_2 as (select A.* from Ptj_Intrari A   WHERE 1=1 AND '2019-10-01' <= A.Ziua AND A.Ziua <= '2019-10-31' )
                                SELECT *,
                                (SELECT ',Ziua' + CASE WHEN Y.Zi <= X.F10023 THEN CONVERT(nvarchar(10), DAY(Y.Zi)) END
                                FROM F100 X
                                INNER JOIN tblZile Y ON '2019-10-01' <= Y.Zi AND Y.Zi <= '2019-10-31'
                                WHERE X.F10003=A.F10003
                                FOR XML PATH ('')) AS ZileLucrate,
                                (SELECT ',Ziua' + CASE WHEN Y.Zi < CONVERT(date,X.F10022) OR CONVERT(date,X.F10023) < Y.Zi THEN CONVERT(nvarchar(10), DAY(Y.Zi)) END
                                FROM F100 X
                                INNER JOIN tblZile Y ON '2019-10-01' <= Y.Zi AND Y.Zi <= '2019-10-31'
                                WHERE X.F10003=A.F10003
                                FOR XML PATH ('')) AS ZileGri
                                FROM (
                                SELECT TOP 100 PERCENT COALESCE(3,1) AS IdRol, st.Denumire AS StarePontaj, isnull(zabs.Ramase, 0) as ZileCONeefectuate, isnull(zlp.Ramase, 0) as ZLPNeefectuate, A.F100901, CAST('2019-10-01' AS datetime) AS ZiuaInc, 
                                CONVERT(VARCHAR, A.F10022, 103) AS DataInceput, CONVERT(VARCHAR, ddp.DataPlecare, 103) AS DataSfarsit,  A.F10008 + ' ' + A.F10009 AS AngajatNume, C.Id AS IdContract, 
                                Y.Norma, Y.F10002, Y.F10004, Y.F10005, Y.F10006, Y.F10007, 
                                C.Denumire AS DescContract, ISNULL(C.OreSup,0) AS OreSup, ISNULL(C.Afisare,1) AS Afisare, 
                                B.F100958, B.F100959,
                                H.F00507 AS "Sectie",I.F00608 AS "Dept", S2.F00204 AS "Companie", S3.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", S4.F00406 AS "Filiala", S7.F00709 AS "Subdept", S8.F00810 AS "Birou", F10061, F10062, CTG.Denumire as Categorie,
                                ISNULL(K.Culoare,'#FFFFFFFF') AS Culoare, K.Denumire AS StareDenumire,
                                A.F10078 AS Angajator, DR.F08903 AS TipContract, 
                                (SELECT MAX(US.F70104) FROM USERS US WHERE US.F10003=X.F10003) AS EID,
                                dn.Norma AS AvansNorma, 
                                CASE WHEN Y.Norma <> dn.Norma THEN (SELECT MAX(F70406) FROM F704 WHERE F70403=pvt.F10003 AND F70404=6 AND YEAR(F70406)=2019 AND MONTH(F70406)=10) ELSE '2100-01-01' END AS AvansData,

		                        LEFT JOIN Ptj_tblStari st on st.Id = x.IdStare
		                        left join SituatieZileAbsente zabs on zabs.F10003 = x.F10003 and zabs.An = x.An and zabs.IdAbsenta = (select Id from Ptj_tblAbsente where DenumireScurta = 'CO')
		                        left join SituatieZLP zlp on zlp.F10003 = x.F10003 and zlp.An = x.An
                                INNER JOIN (SELECT F10003 , [2019-10-01] AS "Ziua1", [2019-10-02] AS "Ziua2", [2019-10-03] AS "Ziua3", [2019-10-04] AS "Ziua4", [2019-10-05] AS "Ziua5", [2019-10-06] AS "Ziua6", [2019-10-07] AS "Ziua7", [2019-10-08] AS "Ziua8", [2019-10-09] AS "Ziua9", [2019-10-10] AS "Ziua10", [2019-10-11] AS "Ziua11", [2019-10-12] AS "Ziua12", [2019-10-13] AS "Ziua13", [2019-10-14] AS "Ziua14", [2019-10-15] AS "Ziua15", [2019-10-16] AS "Ziua16", [2019-10-17] AS "Ziua17", [2019-10-18] AS "Ziua18", [2019-10-19] AS "Ziua19", [2019-10-20] AS "Ziua20", [2019-10-21] AS "Ziua21", [2019-10-22] AS "Ziua22", [2019-10-23] AS "Ziua23", [2019-10-24] AS "Ziua24", [2019-10-25] AS "Ziua25", [2019-10-26] AS "Ziua26", [2019-10-27] AS "Ziua27", [2019-10-28] AS "Ziua28", [2019-10-29] AS "Ziua29", [2019-10-30] AS "Ziua30", [2019-10-31] AS "Ziua31" FROM 
                                (SELECT F10003, ValStr, Ziua From Ptj_Intrari_2 WHERE '2019-10-01' <= CAST(Ziua AS date) AND CAST(Ziua AS date) <= '2019-10-31') AS source  
                                PIVOT  (MAX(ValStr) FOR Ziua IN (  [2019-10-01], [2019-10-02], [2019-10-03], [2019-10-04], [2019-10-05], [2019-10-06], [2019-10-07], [2019-10-08], [2019-10-09], [2019-10-10], [2019-10-11], [2019-10-12], [2019-10-13], [2019-10-14], [2019-10-15], [2019-10-16], [2019-10-17], [2019-10-18], [2019-10-19], [2019-10-20], [2019-10-21], [2019-10-22], [2019-10-23], [2019-10-24], [2019-10-25], [2019-10-26], [2019-10-27], [2019-10-28], [2019-10-29], [2019-10-30], [2019-10-31] )) pvt
                                ) pvt ON X.F10003=pvt.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=X.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN F1001 B ON A.F10003=B.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT R.F10003, MIN(R.Ziua) AS ZiuaMin FROM Ptj_Intrari_2 R WHERE YEAR(R.Ziua)= 2019 AND MONTH(R.Ziua)= 10 GROUP BY R.F10003) Q ON Q.F10003=A.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Intrari_2 Y ON A.F10003=Y.F10003 AND Y.Ziua=Q.ZiuaMin
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_tblStariPontaj K ON K.Id = ISNULL(X.IdStare,1) 
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Contracte C on C.Id = Y.IdContract 
                                LEFT JOIN F089 DR ON DR.F08902 = A.F1009741 
                                LEFT JOIN viewCategoriePontaj CTG ON A.F10003 = CTG.F10003
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiNorma(X.F10003, '2019-10-31') dn 
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiDataPlecare(X.F10003, '2019-10-31') ddp 

							    LEFT JOIN F002 S2 ON Y.F10002 = S2.F00202
							    LEFT JOIN F003 S3 ON Y.F10004 = S3.F00304
							    LEFT JOIN F004 S4 ON Y.F10005 = S4.F00405

                                LEFT JOIN F008 S8 ON B.F100959 = S8.F00809

                                LEFT JOIN F062 L ON Y.F06204Default=L.F06204

                                LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802

                                WHERE X.An = 2019 AND X.Luna = 10 
                                ORDER BY AngajatNume) A
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A.F10003 IN ( SELECT X.F10003 FROM (  SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup WHERE C.IdSuper =4 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.f10003 UNION SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup INNER JOIN F100Supervizori D ON D.F10003 = B.F10003 AND D.IdSuper = (-1 * C.IdSuper) AND (100 * 2019 + 10 BETWEEN isnull(100 * year(D.DataInceput) + MONTH(D.DataInceput), 190000) AND isnull(100 * year(D.DataSfarsit) + MONTH(D.DataSfarsit), 210000))  WHERE D.IdUser =4 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.F10003) X  WHERE X.F10003 IN (SELECT S.F10003 FROM F100 S WHERE CONVERT(date,S.F10022) <> CONVERT(date,S.F100993)  AND F10022 <= '2019-10-31' AND '2019-10-01' <= F100993 ) GROUP BY X.F10003)

                                INNER JOIN (SELECT F10003 , [2019-09-01] AS "Ziua1", [2019-09-02] AS "Ziua2", [2019-09-03] AS "Ziua3", [2019-09-04] AS "Ziua4", [2019-09-05] AS "Ziua5", [2019-09-06] AS "Ziua6", [2019-09-07] AS "Ziua7", [2019-09-08] AS "Ziua8", [2019-09-09] AS "Ziua9", [2019-09-10] AS "Ziua10", [2019-09-11] AS "Ziua11", [2019-09-12] AS "Ziua12", [2019-09-13] AS "Ziua13", [2019-09-14] AS "Ziua14", [2019-09-15] AS "Ziua15", [2019-09-16] AS "Ziua16", [2019-09-17] AS "Ziua17", [2019-09-18] AS "Ziua18", [2019-09-19] AS "Ziua19", [2019-09-20] AS "Ziua20", [2019-09-21] AS "Ziua21", [2019-09-22] AS "Ziua22", [2019-09-23] AS "Ziua23", [2019-09-24] AS "Ziua24", [2019-09-25] AS "Ziua25", [2019-09-26] AS "Ziua26", [2019-09-27] AS "Ziua27", [2019-09-28] AS "Ziua28", [2019-09-29] AS "Ziua29", [2019-09-30] AS "Ziua30" FROM 
                                (SELECT F10003, ValStr, Ziua From Ptj_Intrari_2 WHERE '2019-09-01' <= CAST(Ziua AS date) AND CAST(Ziua AS date) <= '2019-09-30') AS source  
                                PIVOT  (MAX(ValStr) FOR Ziua IN (  [2019-09-01], [2019-09-02], [2019-09-03], [2019-09-04], [2019-09-05], [2019-09-06], [2019-09-07], [2019-09-08], [2019-09-09], [2019-09-10], [2019-09-11], [2019-09-12], [2019-09-13], [2019-09-14], [2019-09-15], [2019-09-16], [2019-09-17], [2019-09-18], [2019-09-19], [2019-09-20], [2019-09-21], [2019-09-22], [2019-09-23], [2019-09-24], [2019-09-25], [2019-09-26], [2019-09-27], [2019-09-28], [2019-09-29], [2019-09-30] )) pvt
                                ) pvt ON X.F10003=pvt.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=X.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN F1001 B ON A.F10003=B.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT R.F10003, MIN(R.Ziua) AS ZiuaMin FROM Ptj_Intrari_2 R WHERE YEAR(R.Ziua)= 2019 AND MONTH(R.Ziua)= 9 GROUP BY R.F10003) Q ON Q.F10003=A.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Intrari_2 Y ON A.F10003=Y.F10003 AND Y.Ziua=Q.ZiuaMin
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_tblStariPontaj K ON K.Id = ISNULL(X.IdStare,1) 
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Contracte C on C.Id = Y.IdContract 
                                LEFT JOIN F089 DR ON DR.F08902 = A.F1009741 
                                LEFT JOIN viewCategoriePontaj CTG ON A.F10003 = CTG.F10003
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiNorma(X.F10003, '2019-09-30') dn 
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiDataPlecare(X.F10003, '2019-09-30') ddp 

							    LEFT JOIN F002 S2 ON Y.F10002 = S2.F00202
							    LEFT JOIN F003 S3 ON Y.F10004 = S3.F00304
							    LEFT JOIN F004 S4 ON Y.F10005 = S4.F00405

							    LEFT JOIN F005 H ON Y.F10006 = H.F00506
							    LEFT JOIN F006 I ON Y.F10007 = I.F00607

							    LEFT JOIN F007 S7 ON B.F100958 = S7.F00708
                                LEFT JOIN F008 S8 ON B.F100959 = S8.F00809

                                LEFT JOIN F062 L ON Y.F06204Default=L.F06204

                                LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802

                                WHERE X.An = 2019 AND X.Luna = 9 
                                ORDER BY AngajatNume) A
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A.F10003 IN ( SELECT X.F10003 FROM (  SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup WHERE C.IdSuper =4 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.f10003 UNION SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup INNER JOIN F100Supervizori D ON D.F10003 = B.F10003 AND D.IdSuper = (-1 * C.IdSuper) AND (100 * 2019 + 9 BETWEEN isnull(100 * year(D.DataInceput) + MONTH(D.DataInceput), 190000) AND isnull(100 * year(D.DataSfarsit) + MONTH(D.DataSfarsit), 210000))  WHERE D.IdUser =4 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.F10003) X  WHERE X.F10003 IN (SELECT S.F10003 FROM F100 S WHERE CONVERT(date,S.F10022) <> CONVERT(date,S.F100993)  AND F10022 <= '2019-9-30' AND '2019-9-01' <= F100993 ) GROUP BY X.F10003)

Eroarea:   BEGIN TRAN INSERT INTO "Ptj_CereriIstoric"("IdCerere", "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", "IdStare", "IdUser", "Pozitie", "Aprobat", "DataAprobare", USER_NO, TIME, "Inlocuitor", "IdUserInlocuitor", "Culoare")
                                SELECT G.*, 
                                (SELECT "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_tblStari" WHERE "Id" = "IdStare") AS "Culoare"
                                FROM (
                                SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") AS "IdCerere", 
                                4 AS "IdCircuit", "IdSuper", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) AND ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 4 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = 1 THEN 3 ELSE 
                                (CASE WHEN "Total" = (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) THEN 3 ELSE
                                (CASE WHEN ((CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) END) END) END AS "IdStare", 
                                "IdUser", 
                                CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) AS Pozitie, 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100002 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) END AS "Aprobat", 
                                CASE WHEN (0 = 1) THEN (CASE WHEN (CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))) = 1 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) ELSE (CASE WHEN "IdUser" = 100002 THEN GetDate() ELSE NULL END) END AS "DataAprobare", 
                                100002 AS USER_NO, GetDate() AS TIME, 0 AS "Inlocuitor", NULL AS "IdUserInlocuitor" 
                                FROM (SELECT W.*, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY 1) AS "Total" FROM ( SELECT 0 AS "Index", F70102 AS "IdUser", 0 AS "IdSuper", 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM USERS WHERE F10003=2 UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 1 AS "Index", IdUser, -2 AS IdSuper, 0 AS "Inlocuitor" FROM (
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2) AND IdUser = 100002
                                        UNION ALL
                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -2)

                                        SELECT TOP 1 IdUser FROM F100Supervizori WHERE F10003 = 2 AND IdSuper = (-1 * -4)

                                OUTPUT Inserted.Id, Inserted.IdStare SELECT (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri")  AS "Id", 2 AS "F10003", 22 AS "IdAbsenta", CONVERT(date,'2019-11-27') AS "DataInceput", CONVERT(date,'2019-11-27') AS "DataSfarsit", 1 AS "NrZile", NULL AS "NrZileViitor", NULL AS "Observatii", (SELECT TOP 1 "IdStare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "IdStare", 4 AS "IdCircuit", 100002 AS "UserIntrod", (SELECT TOP 1 "Culoare" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "Culoare", NULL AS "Inlocuitor", (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "TotalSuperCircuit", (SELECT TOP 1 "Pozitie" FROM "Ptj_CereriIstoric" WHERE "Aprobat"=1 AND "IdCerere"=(SELECT COALESCE(MAX(COALESCE("Id",0)),0) + 1 FROM "Ptj_Cereri") ) AS "Pozitie",  NULL AS "TrimiteLa", 0,5 AS "NrOre", NULL AS "AreAtas",null  AS "CampExtra1" ,null  AS "CampExtra2" ,null  AS "CampExtra3" ,null  AS "CampExtra4" ,null  AS "CampExtra5" ,null  AS "CampExtra6" ,null  AS "CampExtra7" ,null  AS "CampExtra8" ,null  AS "CampExtra9" ,null  AS "CampExtra10" ,null  AS "CampExtra11" ,null  AS "CampExtra12" ,null  AS "CampExtra13" ,null  AS "CampExtra14" ,null  AS "CampExtra15" ,null  AS "CampExtra16" ,null  AS "CampExtra17" ,null  AS "CampExtra18" ,null  AS "CampExtra19" ,null  AS "CampExtra20" ; COMMIT TRAN
